{"tid":666862,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"在台灣何必租車","createTime":"2018-05-16T09:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T07:56:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1b3772bec24a8ed1edd9875e26a67fd52c87bb3c","tid":666862,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:08:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180516/20391746\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F20391746&d=tHclZjdFv0JrE21jMsQuEDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=0065d0f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F20391746&h=1c7d8ec1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180516/20391746</a><br />\n<br />\n在台灣何必租車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180516/large/e8810a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180516%2Flarge%2Fe8810a.jpg&h=29be72d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n港人台灣租車自駕遊，自撞令出租車輛嚴重損毀，惹出一身蟻，很明顯是沒有購買total loss的車全保。據悉事主曾經任職保險公司，購買保險的意識理應比一般人更強，奇怪竟然連這種錢都不捨得支出。<br />\n<br />\n我在眾多國家租過車，只選擇大公司。但所有租車公司只強制要求顧客購買第三保，從不強迫顧客購買車全保。事實上車輛損毀的比例相當少，所以很多人貪小便宜就不買了。不買全保的話，租車時車行會和顧客一起驗車，提供一份很詳細的資料，記錄車身上舊有的「傷痕」，若還車時增添新的「傷痕」，租車者就要負責賠償。<br />\n<br />\n雙方一起驗完車，簽名作實。文明國家尊重契約精神，簽了約，就是一份承諾。若買車全保，就會省去驗車程序，不管顧客交回甚麼車，即使全車盡毀，也由保險公司提供賠償。<br />\n<br />\n外出旅遊，首要目的是玩得安心。我喜歡駕駛，但從不在台灣租車，主要是對其他道路使用者不放心，台灣人駕機車，毫無章法，像行路一樣，喜歡怎麼走就怎麼走，喜歡急停或轉彎也隨意得很。萬一發生碰撞意外，處理方式也跟歐美加澳日本等國不一樣，人情與制度混淆。我的原則是君子不立危牆之下，所以去台灣，從不租車。<br />\n<br />\n去台灣，包車很方便。在街上攔一輛的士，跟司機聊一陣，信得過司機駕駛態度和人品的，直接問司機做不做包車生意就行。司機多數樂意。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk <br />\n<br />\n網頁：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowaiyin.yoyoko&d=tHclZjdFv0JrE21jMsQuEDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=dea1bf87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko</a>"},{"pid":"90901d7798d3bb6cc6ef4ae161c12f76e13c89b3","tid":666862,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:15:27.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"7906a0197503c6a12fd943098456907d825ea86f","tid":666862,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T06:18:03.000Z","msg":"ON9<br />\n若買車全保，就會省去驗車程序，不管顧客交回甚麼車，即使全車盡毀，也由保險公司提供賠償。<br />\n<br />\n交車會驗<br />\n你花左係要call警察,保險公司先會理"},{"pid":"c18a87d4a16f1185b7ca2c67c0b49ab9ef5b78ad","tid":666862,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"on9 鍾意自己揸車周圍去唔得既<br />\n你不如寫 旅行 何必去台灣啦"},{"pid":"87586272acb28d70d7d77daf97fe49012c969906","tid":666862,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T06:29:31.000Z","msg":"好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算買齊保險都一樣會一齊驗車<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4070ebb8ce858b14ef0583b87b2e783658be486","tid":666862,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"高慧然  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5962bfe360472001da25b9913ea662c2375b702a","tid":666862,"uid":163758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c18a87d4a16f1185b7ca2c67c0b49ab9ef5b78ad","tid":666862,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"on9 鍾意自己揸車周圍去唔得既<br />\n你不如寫 旅行 何必去台灣啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:56:05.000Z","msg":"agger"}]}